Evan Summerfield from Devon died from meningitis just 12 hours after laughing for the first time . 
  He had woken from a nap with a rash stretching from his head to his belly-button . 
  He was diagnosed with meningoccal septicaemia and died at Derriford Hospital in Plymouth . 
  His parents Shannon Summerfield and Kris Adams are devastated by his death . 
 